nting success\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"andFanny Blankers-Koen\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"four goldson\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"fourOlympicstrack titles\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why four?\\\"\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LylestoldThe Times.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LylestoldThe Times\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, there have been multiple doubles, not a lot, but there have been plenty.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple doubles\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can grab three but Bolt has done that.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bolt\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can do two Olympics in a row, but Bolt has done that too.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two Olympics\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"Bolt\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A field event?\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"A field event\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nope, been done.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I really have to look.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's left on the table that could put me on my Mount Rushmore, make people say, 'Not only was he great, but he did something that has not been done'?\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"my Mount Rushmore\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I want and expect are two different things.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two different things\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I expect to get multiple gold medals but what I want is four.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple gold medals\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can definitely put a downpayment on two, but relays are a bit tricky.\\\"\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a downpayment\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"relays\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dutchwoman Blankers-Koen won golds in the 100m, 200m, 80m hurdles and 4x100m in London, her only Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999993774509, \"rank\": 6.179694976834699e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dutchwoman Blankers-Koen\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"200m\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"hurdles\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"4x100m\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles faces a battle making it into the defending champion USA's relay quartet over the longer distance, though the schedule does allow him to fit all four events in.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9992172345280306, \"rank\": 0.0004135605317569651, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"a battle\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the defending champion\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"the longer distance\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the schedule\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"all four events\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The heats for the 4x400m at the Stade de France take place the morning after his 200m individual final,with the medal race a day later on August 10.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2227, \"end\": 2242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The heats\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x400m\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"his 200m individual final\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal race\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been criticised, though, for trying to force his way into the quartet, pulling out of the 4x400m at the recent World Relays in the Bahamas after team mates complained about his involvement at the Indoors in Glasgow.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2483, \"end\": 2490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999570264, \"rank\": 4.305475213768074e-11, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}, {\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9993394709128166, \"rank\": 0.0006609607467605262, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"the quartet\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent World Relays\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"team mates\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"his involvement\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the Indoors\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of people in the US were very, very, very upset that I ran the 4x4,\\\" Lyles said.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2593, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9997030167694781, \"rank\": 0.00029670347797325786, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x4\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not give all the details but there were coaches who coached athletes that were on the 4x4 that did not get to run that were upset about that.\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the details\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x4\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They complained to higher-ups about the decision.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"higher-ups\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The higher-ups decided to take action.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The higher-ups\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether this will happen again, I do not know.\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are they going to make new rule changes?\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new rule changes\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the way that the rules are set up now is anybody who is actually on the team can be in the relay.\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3011}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3052}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to keep doing what I do.\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the relay coach's decision.\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay coach's decision\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to tell them the same thing - \\\"If you want to use me, I am here, if you do not, that's fine\\\".\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not going to have hurt feelings about it.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"feelings\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will be training specifically for the 100 and 200 and be as strong as possible in the 400.\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in the best in shape I have ever been in my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3527, \"end\": 3538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999996077804, \"rank\": 3.656170588218221e-10, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"inP